CHAPTER 2.

Q1. Line plot(1)

#      
maximum <- data %>% 
  group_by(confirmed_date) %>% 
  summarise(
    confirmed_number = n()
  ) %>% 
  mutate(
    max_index = which.max(confirmed_number),
    max_date = confirmed_date[max_index],
    max_num = confirmed_number[max_index]
  ) %>% 
  select(max_date, max_num) %>% 
  head(1)

#   confirmed_number         
#1 6  confirmed_number   ,
#    6    confirmed_number  .

data %>% 
  group_by(confirmed_date) %>% 
  summarise(
    confirmed_number = n()
  ) %>%
 ggplot(aes(confirmed_date, confirmed_number)) +
  geom_line(color = "lightblue") + 
  annotate("point",
           x= maximum$max_date, y=maximum$max_num,
           color = 'navy') +
  annotate("text",
           x = maximum$max_date-20, y=maximum$max_num, 
           label = sprintf("%s(%d)", maximum$max_date, maximum$max_num),
           fontface = 2,
           color = 'navy') +
  labs(title="  \n- ") +
  theme_classic() +
  theme(plot.title = element_text(hjust=0.5, face = "bold"))
